title: GRSE Notification 2025 - Apply Online for 226 Apprentice Posts
description: The Garden Reach Shipbuilders & Engineers (GRSE) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 226 Graduate Apprentices, Technician Apprentices, Trade Apprentices, and HR Trainee Jobs. Interested and eligibile candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their 10th pass, ITI, B.E./B.
